page.title: 09A PRIMARY CHILDS DAY
page.content: I get up and dress at 7.30.I wear a navy skirt and jumper and a white blouse.I have a cup of tea and some cereal.I get ready for school.During school we have maths,english and other work.Break is at 10.30.Then we do some other work until 11.55,then it is dinner break.After the bell has rang we go in.We have P.E.which in the summer is mostly rounders.Break is at 2.15. As it is wednesday I go to my violin lesson. At 3.00 I tidy up.I go home at 3.30 Then I take the dog out with my mum. When I come back I have my tea.Then I either go round my nannaÂ£s or watch television.I read a little bit in bed.
